Class ComparableCall<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dm.jrt.retrofit.ComparableCall<T>

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, retrofit2.Call<T>

    public class ComparableCall<T>
extends Object
implements retrofit2.Call<T>
    Decorator implementation making a call instance comparable (that is, equals(Object) and hashCode() methods are properly implemented.

    Created by davide-maestroni on 03/25/2016.
